{"tid":1464462,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"佢係鬼！！大家認住佢！！","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:04:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:12:18.000Z","uid":124235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c781e93e88469ca6b2ac6f545a4f9f373c2bdbb5","tid":1464462,"uid":124235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:04:12.000Z","msg":"自從有鬼之後大家既神經都好易被觸動，入機場既活動第一日係好成功，但今日似乎出現左D唔受控既情況<br />\n<br />\n大家明明係以和理非既主義入去，想要成功，我諗大家係機場入面要有共識同一D不成文既規定黎防止自亂陣腳<br />\n<br />\n舉例：<br />\n1. 不妨礙任何救援工作<br />\n2. 不攻擊任何人（自衛除外）<br />\n3. 不直接阻礙旅客（我地唔係搞緊不合作運動）<br />\n<br />\n主要係想俾D建議，如果大家都有D共識既時候，係人係鬼大家一清二楚，依次公安事件係好好既借鑒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdb77e7387f2b761b279a6f1c248726eab1e489a","tid":1464462,"uid":124235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:06:57.000Z","msg":"10，推一下，鬧我都無所謂，但唔想機場集會咁快玩完"},{"pid":"cbf549c9d490ec4a9abefe3901c757d935714641","tid":1464462,"uid":124235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdb77e7387f2b761b279a6f1c248726eab1e489a","tid":1464462,"uid":124235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:06:57.000Z","msg":"10，推一下，鬧我都無所謂，但唔想機場集會咁快玩完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:07:23.000Z","msg":"9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5ac8cf324e1e725509bea9e4dfb0e6af81b656c","tid":1464462,"uid":124235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbf549c9d490ec4a9abefe3901c757d935714641","tid":1464462,"uid":124235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdb77e7387f2b761b279a6f1c248726eab1e489a","tid":1464462,"uid":124235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:06:57.000Z","msg":"10，推一下，鬧我都無所謂，但唔想機場集會咁快玩完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:07:23.000Z","msg":"9<im